N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 2051.5 - Administrative review

State Regulations

Persons who may file. Any person aggrieved by an order
issued by a district rent administrator may file a petition for administrative
review (PAR) with the commissioner in the manner provided in Operational

Bulletin Number 84-1 and any supplements thereto. Notes
